item.description:
Today we learn words for doing chores around the house.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
My fitness journey began when I was a young adult & new to the United States. I came from a small country in East Africa called Eritrea where women aren't usually seen outside of their traditional gender role. I never wanted to fit the traditional role. I believe that taking care of my physical health positively affects my mental & spiritual well being. And vice versa. I believe that strong girls are beautiful. What started as a hobby, grew into a passion, now is my way of life. My goal is to empower & inspire women through self-care & fitness - starting with myself.

ela tv presents - Mussie Berhe - Emberwel - Kethal'l - New Eritrean Music 2020
Subscribe today: https://goo.gl/7936J7

Kethal’l (ከጣልል)…?

The ancient history of Eritrea has a vital contribution in shaping the general fabric of today`s regional civilization. The country is an open museum with unprecedented evidence of ancient history known to mankind.

A huge part of Eritrea`s ancient history is not fully studied and understood yet, and this impedes from having exclusive and cohesive information. However, the country is endowed with potentially rich and segmented history.

Eritrea’s present cultural diversity is the result of a long process of cultural evolution. This process has been characterized by the emergence of symbolism, writing systems, trade, agriculture, modernity, cultural pluralism, traditions, beliefs, customs…etc. Henceforth, such cultural trends demonstrate the continuous presence of human settlement in the region since millennia.

The inland civilizations of Eritrea and the Red Sea coast were underpinning the cultural and trade hubs flourished in the region. Hence, many inland civilizations thrived. The Qohaito cultural landscape and the archaeological site of Below Kelow (Matara) which embrace evidence spanning from 2nd millennium BC to 7th Century AD, are among the most renowned ancient cities from the Highlands of Eritrea.

Kethal’l (ከጣልል)…?, an Eritrean creative music video clip featuring love-story, is exceptionally presenting the ancient cultural phenomena of societies residing the Eritrean highlands. The video clip gives an insight into the ancient civilization as well as the lifestyle of the societies inhabiting these places. It further artistically represents, the beauty of the highland’s natural landscape, the archaeological wonders (stone tools, rock arts, standing architecture, dams, cisterns, enigmatic ruins, other artefacts…) and value systems that are central to our understanding of early subsistence, symbolic systems and cultural evolution of the Eritrean highland communities.

Dr Tsegai Medin
Archaeological Heritage Research Branch-AHRB

“Qin Leboch”, literary translated as “Kind Hearts”, is a hidden camera TV show that intends to explore the real responses of the society in real situations of conflict, illegal activities or incidents of susceptibilities. Each program features actors acting out scenes of conflict or illegal activity in public settings while hidden cameras record the scene, and the focus is on whether or not bystanders intervene, and how. item.title: እንዴት አድርገን የአፕል ኬክ ማዘጋጀት እንደምንችል / How to make Apple cake
item.description:
Ingredients

Apple Cake

*1 2/3 cups ( 210 grams) all purpose flour
* 1 teaspoon ( 4 grams) baking powder
* 1/2 teaspoon ( 2 grams ) baking soda
* 1/2 teaspoon ( 2 grams ) kosher salt
* 3 large eggs at room temperature
* 1/2 cup ( 120 ml ) flavorless oil ( safflower, corn , vegetable, or canola )
* 3/4 cup ( 180 grams ) Mascarpone or (whole milk plain yogurt ), at room temperature
* 1 teaspoon ( 4 grams) pure vanilla extract
* 3/4 (150 grams ) granulated white sugar
* 1 Apple 🍎
* 1 teaspoon ground cinnamon ( optional)

Instructions

Preheat your oven to 350 degrees F ( 180 degrees C ) and place the oven rack in the center of the oven. Butter or spray with a non stick butter ( vegetable) spray , an 8 inch ( 18 cm) spring form pan. Line the bottom of the pan with parchment paper. Bake in preheated oven for about 45 to 50 minutes or until toothpick inserted into the center of the cake come out clean. Remove from oven and place on a wire rack to cool.

Abby Lakew, is an African grammy award nominated singer songwriter and actress from Ethiopia and she was born in Gonder, Ethiopia. In 2007 she released her debut studio album ''Manale''. Which featured both English, amharic songs, Ethiopian traditional and dance music and was a reflection of her two identities – Ethiopian and American. In 2012 she released a new single Shikorina followed by Endemewadeh, in 2014 Abererew, 2015 the smash hit Yene Habesha and 2016 Befikir Eskista. In 2012 she landed the leading role in a critically acclaimed Ethiopian Movie called Eyerus. In September 2017 she released her second studio album Yene Habesha.

Abby Lakew, is an African grammy award nominated singer songwriter and actress from Ethiopia and she was born in Gonder, Ethiopia. In 2007 she released her debut studio album ''Manale''. Which featured both English, amharic songs, Ethiopian traditional and dance music and was a reflection of her two identities – Ethiopian and American. In 2012 she released a new single Shikorina followed by Endemewadeh, in 2014 Abererew, 2015 the smash hit Yene Habesha and 2016 Befikir Eskista. In 2012 she landed the leading role in a critically acclaimed Ethiopian Movie called Eyerus. In September 2017 she released her second studio album Yene Habesha.
She is getting ready for her 2018 world tour starting in Ethiopia.

item.title: The fun we had celebrating Ethiopian New Year with friends | እንቁጣጣሽን ከጓደኞቻችን ጋር በደስታ አከበርን፡ መስ.2013
item.description:
We celebrated Ethiopian New Year on September 11, 2020 with our beloved friends. It was the most fun we had on this day and first time we had a party in our house on Ethiopian New Year 😊 It is still 2013 in Ethiopia. Read further down this description to know why!
In this video, we show some of the cultures and traditions on the Ethiopian New Year celebration. Girls go door to door singing (enkutatash enkuan metash…) boys make colorful drawings and also give it as gifts to neighbors, in return they received small changes, big cash, candy or a just a thank you! :D
We also show a small coffee ceremony and have chats about our childhood memories during and around the new year.
Ethiopia has a special Coptic calendar with 13 months. The last month having 5 days except for leap years when it will be 6 days. New year in Ethiopia signifies the end of the rainy season and start of a new school year!
Adey abeba, (a species of plants in the family Asteraseae) start to bloom in the new year and are a prominent symbol of the coming sunny season. New Year celebration in Ethiopia is called Enkutatash እንቁጣጣሽ.

item.title: Semret Russom - Semret Fit - Changing My Mindset
item.description:
Today I share with you a struggle I had with my fitness journey and how I overcame my doubts by changing my mindset.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
My fitness journey began when I was a young adult & new to the United States. I came from a small country in East Africa called Eritrea where women aren't usually seen outside of their traditional gender role. I never wanted to fit the traditional role. I believe that taking care of my physical health positively affects my mental & spiritual well being. And vice versa. I believe that strong girls are beautiful. What started as a hobby, grew into a passion, now is my way of life. My goal is to empower & inspire women through self-care & fitness - starting with myself.

item.title: How To Make Yogurt Cake #yogurtcake / እንዴት አድርገን በእርጎ ኬክ ማዘጋጀት እንደምንችል
item.description:
Ingredients

Yogurt Cake

*1 1/4 cups ( 165 grams) all purpose flour
*1/4 cup ( 30 grams) ground almonds
* 1 tablespoon ( 4 grams) baking powder
* 1/2 teaspoon ( 2 grams ) baking soda
* 1/2 teaspoon ( 2 grams ) kosher salt
* Zest ( outer skin ) of one lemon
* 2 large eggs ( 100 grams out of shell ) at room temperature
* 1/2 cup ( 120 ml ) flavorless oil ( safflower, corn , vegetable, or canola )
* 3/4 cup ( 180 ml ) whole milk plain yogurt , at room temperature
* 1 teaspoon ( 4 grams) pure vanilla extract
* 1 cup ( 200 grams ) granulated white sugar


Instructions

Preheat your oven to 350 degrees F ( 180 degrees C ) and place the oven rack in the center of the oven. Butter or spray with a non stick butter ( vegetable) spray , an 8 inch ( 20cm) spring form pan. Line the bottom of the pan with parchment paper.
In a large bowl stir or whisk together the flour, ground almonds, baking powder, baking soda, salt and lemon zest.
In another bowl, stir or whisk together the egg , oil, yogurt, and vanilla extract, stir in the sugar.
Add the wet ingredients to the dry flour mixture. Stir until just combined scrape the batter into the prepared pan. Bake in preheated oven for about 40 to 45 minutes or until toothpick inserted into the center of the cake come out clean. Remove from oven and place on a wire rack to cool. You can serve this cake plain or with ice cream or lightly sweetened yogurt.

item.description:
“Qin Leboch”, literary translated as “Kind Hearts”, is a hidden camera TV show that intends to explore the real responses of the society in real situations of conflict, illegal activities or incidents of susceptibilities. Each program features actors acting out scenes of conflict or illegal activity in public settings while hidden cameras record the scene, and the focus is on whether or not bystanders intervene, and how. As it is designed to promote positive behavior and good go-getters, it also features a studio segment to endorse constructive comments and postings on social media, and reward a certain amount of money.

“Qin Leboch”, literary translated as “Kind Hearts”, is a hidden camera TV show that intends to explore the real responses of the society in real situations of conflict, illegal activities or incidents of susceptibilities. Each program features actors acting out scenes of conflict or illegal activity in public settings while hidden cameras record the scene, and the focus is on whether or not bystanders intervene, and how. ዝነኛው እና ተወዳጁ ድምፃዊ መስፍን በቀለ ከዚህ ቀደም በሁለት ሙሉ የሙዚቃ አልበም እና በስኬታማ ሀገራዊ ድንቅ ስራዎቹ ብሎም በተለያዩ ነጠላ ዜማዎች ሰምተን የወደድነው አይትን የመሰከርንልተ ተወዳጅ ስራዎችን ሲያቀርብልን እንደነበር ምስክራችን እናተው የጥበብ አክባሪዎች እንደሆናቹ ምንም ጥርጥር የለንም::
ስለዚህ ዛሬም እንደትናቱ ሁሉ (ሚስጥር ነው) በሚል መጠሪያ ነጠላ ዜማ ከብዙ ድካም በኃላ በከፍታ ይዞላቹሁ ብቅ ብሏል::
ይህ ኢትዮጵያዊነትን የሚሰብክ አዲስ ስራ እጅግ በርካታ ባለሞያዎችን ያሳተፈ ሲሆን የመጀመሪያ ቀረፃውን በዋሽንግተን ዲሲ በመስፍን ፊልም ፖሮዳክሽን ካሜራ ቀረፃ አማካኝነት ብዛት ያላቸውን ሰዎች በማሳተፍ ሲከናወን : ብሎም በሎንደን ከተማ በተደረገው የቪዲዬ ቀረፅ (በኪሮሽ) ፊልም ፖሮዳክሽን አማካኝነት ካሜራ ቀረፃ ተከናውኖ ሲያበቃ : ዋናው እና ትልቁን የአንበሳውን ድርሻ በመውሰድ ዳኒኪራ የኪነጥበብ ዳንስ ጉሩፖ የውዝዋዜውን እና ሙሉ ዝግጅቱን ባማረና በደመቀ ሁኔታ : በዳኒኤል ዱላ ዳሬክቲንግ በመመራት እጅግ በርካታ የሙያ ጥበብኞችን በማሳተፍ ደረጃው በጠበቀ ሁኔታ ወደናተ አምሮ እንዲደርስ በአግባቡ የተከወነ ስራ ነው::
ሌላኛው እና ከሌሎቹ እንደ አንደኛው የአንበሳውን ድርሻ ከሚወስደው ዋነኛውና ትልቁ ደሞ የሙዚቃው አቀናባሪ አሌክስ ይለፍ ነው::
ይሄ ወጣት እና ተወዳጅ ባለሙያ በርካታ ተጨማሪ መሳሪያ ተጫዎቾችን በማሳተፍ እዚህ ሙዚቃ ላይ ዜማን ከከሙዚቃ ጋር አዋህዶ ከሚጣፍጥ ቅንብር ጋር ህይወት የዘራበት ጉራማይሌ ልጅ ነው::
ታድያ ይሄ ሁሉ ነገር ግጥጥሞሹ ምን ይሆን በማለት ሚስጥሩን በመረዳት ብሎም ለእናተ ለማሳወቅ በከፍተኛ ፍላጎት ወጪ በማውጣት ወስነን የአርቲስቶቻችን ነፅብራቅ የሆነው ምነው ሸዋ ቲዩብ ይሄን ትልቅ ስራ ለሀገር ወዳድ ኢትዮጵያንዊን የጥበብ አፍቃሪዎች : እና ለቻናላችን ቤተሰቦች ይደርስ ዘንድ ስናቀርብ በታላቅ ኩራት ነው::
ምነው ሸዋ ኢንተርቴመንት

"ሚስጥር ነው"
የአንድነታችን ሚስጥሩ ኢትዬጲያዊነት የአሸናፊነት ምልክት ረቂቅ ሚስጥር ነው:: ሀገራችን ከውጪ የመጣባትን ወረራ በታሪኳ አንድም ጊዜ ሳትሸነፍ ለሀያላን ሀገሮች ሳትንበረከክ በጀግኖች ልጆቾ መሰዋትነት እንደወርቅ በእሳት ተፈትና ልዕልናዋን: ያስከበረቸ ታፍራና ተከብራ የኖረች ወደፊትም የምትኖር ታላቅ ሚስጥረ እግዚአብሔር ያላት: ኢትዮጵያ ቀደምት ምድረ ገነት ሀገር ናት::
ማስታወሻ
ይህ የጥበብ ስራዬ ማስታወሻነቱ ኢትዮጵያችንን በደም እና በአጥንታቸው አስከብረው እነሱ መሰዋት በመሆን በክብር ላቆዩልን ጀግኖች እባቶቻችን እና አይቶቻችን እንዲሁም በጀግነታቸው ወደር ለማይገኝላቸው በየዘመናቸው ገድል ለፈፀሙ አሁንም በህይወት ለሚገኙ ኩራቶቻችን (የካራማራው) ፈርጦች እስከ ዛሬ በጀግነታቸው ሳይዘመርላቸው ለኖሩ እንደ አሊ በርኪ ደፋር እና ቆራጥ ጀግና ልጆቾዋ አንዲሁም ለአባቴ መቶ አለቃ በቀለ ፉርጋሳ የክብር ማስታወሻዬ ይሁንልኝ::
መስፍን በቀለ

Abby Lakew, is an African grammy award nominated singer songwriter and actress from Ethiopia and she was born in Gonder, Ethiopia. In 2007 she released her debut studio album ''Manale''. Which featured both English, amharic songs, Ethiopian traditional and dance music and was a reflection of her two identities – Ethiopian and American. In 2012 she released a new single Shikorina followed by Endemewadeh, in 2014 Abererew, 2015 the smash hit Yene Habesha and 2016 Befikir Eskista. item.title: Semret Russom - Body Parts & Loving Yourself
item.description:
Today we learn about body parts.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
My fitness journey began when I was a young adult & new to the United States. I came from a small country in East Africa called Eritrea where women aren't usually seen outside of their traditional gender role. I never wanted to fit the traditional role. I believe that taking care of my physical health positively affects my mental & spiritual well being. And vice versa. I believe that strong girls are beautiful. What started as a hobby, grew into a passion, now is my way of life. My goal is to empower & inspire women through self-care & fitness - starting with myself.

item.title: በርበሬ አዘገጃጀት በውጭ ሀገር/ ቤተስብ ማስቸገር, ተሽክሞ መምጣት ቀረ/ በቀላሉ በቤታችን እናዘጋጅ/ /How to Prepare Berbere/
item.description:
የበርበሬ አዘገጃጀት በውጪ ሀገር
በጣም ቀላል ነው በቤታችን ለማዘጋጀት በተለይ በእሁን ስአት ከኢትዮጵያ ለማስመጣት በከበደበት
ስዓት ቤተስብ ከምናስቸግር እንዲ በቀላሉ በቤታችን ማዘጋጀት እንችላለን
አሁን ክረምት ስለሆነ ፀሃይ ስለማናገኝ በኦቭናችን ማድረቅ እችላለን
ኦቭናችንን በሎ ላይ እድርገን ማድረቅ መጠቀቅ ያለብን ቶሎ ቶሎ መነካካትና ማየት ይገባናል
በርበሬው እንደ ኢትዮጵያውያ አያቃጥልም በጣም ቀይም አይደለም በተረፈ ጣህሙ ልዩ ነው
ጥያቄ ካላቹ ከመንት ላይ ያስፍሩ
አዲስ ከሆኑ ለቻናሌ ስብስክራይብ በማድረግ ቤተስብ ይሁኑ ላይክ ሼር በማድረግ ለሌላ ስው እንዲደርስ ያድርጉ
Berebere / Red pepper
Ingredients
1.1 pounds paprika paper /በርበሬ
1/3 Black cardamom / ኮረሪማ
1/3 Oregano / ኮስረት
1whole garlic 🧄/ 1 ሙሉ ነጭ ሽኩርት
1 Red onion /ቀይ ሽንኩርት
1 fresh ginger / ዝንጅብል
2 tablespoon coriander/ ድንብላል
2 tablespoon Black Cumin seed
2 tablespoon Ajawan seed / ነጭ አዝሙድ
2 tablespoon black pepper / ቁንዶ በርበሬ
2 tablespoon salt/ ጨው
1 whole rosemary for taste/ የመጥበሻ ቅጠል

Abby Lakew, is an African grammy award nominated singer songwriter and actress from Ethiopia and she was born in Gonder, Ethiopia. In 2007 she released her debut studio album ''Manale''. Which featured both English, amharic songs, Ethiopian traditional and dance music and was a reflection of her two identities – Ethiopian and American. In 2012 she released a new single Shikorina followed by Endemewadeh, in 2014 Abererew, 2015 the smash hit Yene Habesha and 2016 Befikir Eskista. In 2012 she landed the leading role in a critically acclaimed Ethiopian Movie called Eyerus. In September 2017 she released her second studio album Yene Habesha.
She is getting ready for her 2018 world tour starting in Ethiopia.

item.title: በ35 ደቂቃ የቱና አሳ ስቴክ ከስኳር ድንች ጋር/How to make tuna steak with sweet potato
item.description:
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/lelliyocooks/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Lelliyo-cooks-107966270944301
Recipe:
3 Tuna steaks (ሶስት የቱና ስቴክ)
1 TBS olive oil (አንድ የሾርባ ማኒኪያ የወይራ ዘይት)
2 TBS lemon juice (ሁለት የሾርባ ማንኪያ የሎሚ ጭማቂ)
3-4 Garlic Cloves (ከሶስት አስከ አራት የነጭሽንኩርት ፍሬ)
1/4 teaspoon salt (አንድ አራተኛ የሻይ ማንኪያ ጨው)
1/4 teaspoon black pepper (አንድ አራተኛ የሻይ ማንኪያ ቁንዶ በርበሬ)
2 TBS fresh thyme (ሁለት የሾርባ ማንኪያ ጦስኝ)
For the sweet potato
2 purple sweet potato (ሁለት የስኳር ድንች)
cinnamon (ቀርፋ)
2 TBS unsalted butter (ሁለት የሾርባ ማንኪያ የገበታ ቅቤ)

item.description:
የሃይማኖት መምህራን በሕጻናት ላይ እየደረሰ ያለውን ወሲባዊ ጥቃት ዝም ሊባል የማይገባው ነው ሲሉ አወገዙ።

Petition‎ link :-https://avaaz.org/en/community_petiti...

ወንዶችና ሴቶች ህጻናት በመደፈር ከሚደርስባቸው የሰዕብና ስብራት በጠንካራ የሕግ ማዕቀፍና አፈፃፀም እንዲጠበቁልኝ እዚህ ቅፅ ላይ በመፈረም አቤቱታዬን ለመንግስት አቀርባለሁ! ይህንን ቅፅ ስፈርም አስገድዶ መድፈርና ወሲባዊ ጥቃት አሰቃቂ የሰብዓዊ መብት ጥሰት መሆኑን በመገንዘብ የኢትዮጵያ ፌደራላዊ ዴሞክራሲያዊ ሪፑብሊክ መንግስትን በህዝብ ተወካዮች ምክር ቤት በኩል የወንጀለኛ መቅጫ ሕግ አንቀፆችን፤አንቀፅ 620(1)፣ አንቀፅ 620(2)(ሀ)፣ አንቀፅ 620(3)፣ አንቀፅ 626 (1) እና(4ሀ) እንዲያሻሻል እጠይቃለሁ።
በዚህምመሰረት፣
* ሴቶች ላይ ለሚደርሱ የመደፈርና ወሲባዊ ጥቃቶች የጣለው የእስራት ቅጣት ከፍ ብሎ ከ20 ዓመት ፅኑ እስራት በመጀመር እስከ እድሜ ልክ ፅኑ እስራት ቅጣት ከፍ እንዲደረግና የገንዘብ ቅጣትንም እንዲያካትት እጠይቃለሁ።
* ጥቃቱ በሴትና ወንድ ህፃናት ላይ በደረሰ ጊዜ የጣለው የእስራት ቅጣት ከፍ ብሎ ከእድሜ ልክ ፅኑ እስራት እስከሞት በሚደርስ እንዲያስቀጣ ማሻሻያ እንዲደረግበት እጠይቃለሁ።

Abby Lakew, is an African grammy award nominated singer songwriter and actress from Ethiopia and she was born in Gonder, Ethiopia. In 2007 she released her debut studio album ''Manale''. Which featured both English, amharic songs, Ethiopian traditional and dance music and was a reflection of her two identities – Ethiopian and American. In 2012 she released a new single Shikorina followed by Endemewadeh, in 2014 Abererew, 2015 the smash hit Yene Habesha and 2016 Befikir Eskista. In 2012 she landed the leading role in a critically acclaimed Ethiopian Movie called Eyerus. In September 2017 she released her second studio album Yene Habesha.
She is getting ready for her 2018 world tour starting in Ethiopia.

Abby Lakew, is an African grammy award nominated singer songwriter and actress from Ethiopia and she was born in Gonder, Ethiopia. In 2007 she released her debut studio album ''Manale''. Which featured both English, amharic songs, Ethiopian traditional and dance music and was a reflection of her two identities – Ethiopian and American. In 2012 she released a new single Shikorina followed by Endemewadeh, in 2014 Abererew, 2015 the smash hit Yene Habesha and 2016 Befikir Eskista. In 2012 she landed the leading role in a critically acclaimed Ethiopian Movie called Eyerus. In September 2017 she released her second studio album Yene Habesha.

“Qin Leboch”, literary translated as “Kind Hearts”, is a hidden camera TV show that intends to explore the real responses of the society in real situations of conflict, illegal activities or incidents of susceptibilities. Each program features actors acting out scenes of conflict or illegal activity in public settings while hidden cameras record the scene, and the focus is on whether or not bystanders intervene, and how. “Qin Leboch”, literary translated as “Kind Hearts”, is a hidden camera TV show that intends to explore the real responses of the society in real situations of conflict, illegal activities or incidents of susceptibilities. Each program features actors acting out scenes of conflict or illegal activity in public settings while hidden cameras record the scene, and the focus is on whether or not bystanders intervene, and how. As it is designed to promote positive behavior and good go-getters, it also features a studio segment to endorse constructive comments and postings on social media, and reward a certain amount of money.
